    "title": "Mwana wa Mtu",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "mwana wa mtu",
    "language": "swh",
    "content": "<p>Kifungu cha Kiebrania na Kiaramu &quot;Mwana wa Mtu&quot; kinamaanisha &quot;binadamu.&quot; Hata hivyo, yule anayefananishwa na &quot;Mwana wa Mtu&quot; katika <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan7:13-Dan7:14\">Danieli 7:13–14</a>, anaonekana kuwa zaidi ya binadamu wa kawaida. Utambulisho wake halisi haujatolewa, lakini jukumu lake liko wazi. Juu amemchagua kutawala ufalme wa milele na wa ulimwengu wote juu ya mataifa yote. Pia anawakilisha watu wake, watu watakatifu wa Juu. Wao watashiriki katika ufalme wa Mwana wa mtu huyu juu ya watu na mataifa yote (tazama <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan7:22\">Danieli 7:22</a>).</p><p>Tukio linalomhusu huyu Mwana wa mtu linaonyesha sifa zake za kimungu. Maelezo &quot;akija na mawingu ya mbinguni&quot; katika <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan7:13\">Danieli 7:13</a> yanatuonyesha kwamba anakuja kutoka mbinguni (linganisha <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps68:4\">Zaburi 68:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps97:2\">97:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Nah1:3\">Nahumu 1:3</a>). Katika kitabu cha Kutoka, Bwana Mungu alijifunika na wingu (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod19:9\">Kutoka 19:9</a>). Watu wa Mungu watafufuka kwenda mawinguni Yesu atakaporudi (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess4:17\">1 Wathesalonike 4:17</a>), kama vile alivyopokelewa katika wingu alipokwenda mbinguni (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts1:9\">Matendo 1:9</a>). Huyu Mwana wa mtu anapokea ufalme wake kwa unyenyekevu na utakatifu, si kwa kuutwaa kwa kiburi. Yeye ni kinyume cha tabia na pembe ndogo (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan7:8\">Danieli 7:8</a>).</p><p>Yesu anajitaja kama Mwana wa Mtu (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt24:30\">Mathayo 24:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:24\">26:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark13:26\">Marko 13:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke21:27\">Luka 21:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John12:34\">Yohana 12:34</a>; tazama pia <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts7:56\">Matendo 7:56</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb2:6\">Waebrania 2:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev1:13\">Ufunuo 1:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev14:14\">14:14</a>). <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev1:7\">Ufunuo 1:7</a> pia inamhusisha mtu huyu na Yesu Kristo, ambaye aliteswa kwa ajili ya dhambi zetu. Mungu Baba alimpa Yesu mamlaka yote na nguvu za kutawala kila kitu na kufikia watu kutoka mataifa na falme zote (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan7:14\">Danieli 7:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt28:18\">Mathayo 28:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt28:19-Matt28:20\">19–20</a>). Mungu alimwita Abrahamu kuunda taifa kubwa kupitia watu wake na kubariki mataifa yote kupitia yeye (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen12:1-Gen12:3\">Mwanzo 12:1–3</a>). Yesu alitimiza ahadi hii.</p><p><u>Sehemu za Kujifunza Zaidi</u></p><p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan7:13-Dan7:14\">Danieli 7:13–14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt24:30\">Mathayo 24:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:24\">26:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark13:26\">Marko 13:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke21:27\">Luka 21:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John12:34\">Yohana 12:34</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev1:13\">Ufunuo 1:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev14:14\">14:14</a></p>",
